This is 2 on 3.

00:03:55.910 --> 00:03:57.740
This is 2 on 4, et cetera,
et cetera.

00:03:57.740 --> 00:04:01.000
So each point represents
a fraction.

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:04.490
And you've kind of covered every
single possible fraction

00:04:04.490 --> 00:04:05.840
that there is, right?

